# Part Configurator Integration Design Document

## Executive Summary

This document outlines the comprehensive design for integrating a Part Configurator module into the existing industrial parts catalog system. The Part Configurator will enable users to find compatible parts based on their specific equipment, enhancing the user experience and improving part discovery accuracy.

## 1. Part Configurator Component Architecture

### 1.1 Component Hierarchy

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[ProductsPageClient] --> B[FilterSidebar]
    A --> C[PartConfigurator]
    A --> D[ProductCard]
    
    C --> E[EquipmentSelector]
    C --> F[CompatibilityFilter]
    C --> G[PartResults]
    C --> H[CompatibilityMatrix]
    
    E --> I[EquipmentSearch]
    E --> J[EquipmentBrowse]
    E --> K[EquipmentCard]
    
    F --> L[CompatibilityStatus]
